*2 [[Antidote++]] or [[Superantipoison]] (or replace with twice the number of [[Sanfew serum|Sanfews]])
*6+ [[Blighted super restore]] (can bring more or fewer)
*High healing food primarily for escaping player-killers. A mix of [[Manta ray|Manta rays]] and [[Cooked karambwan]] is recommended as both can be consumed in the same tick.
*4+ [[Saradomin brew|Saradomin brews]]
*[[Imbued heart]] (ensure the item is protected on death)
*100+ casts or [[Blighted ancient ice sack]] for [[Ice Blitz]], [[Ice Barrage]], or [[Entangle]]
*1 or 2 [[Stamina potion]]s for escaping [[player-killing|player-killers]] and during kills, especially if finishing a kill after running out of binds
*[[Wilderness sword 1]] or better, [[Knife]] or [[Slash weapons|slash weapon]] if running from Edgeville lever
*[[Lockpick]], for escaping into the magic axe hut
*[[Black d'hide body]] and [[Black d'hide chaps|chaps]], for tanking player killers
*[[Looting bag]]

